These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, techno
1. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, social-worker
1. the social-worker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Job   | freelancer | social-worker |

 #################################

 
